titleHowToImport: How to view/edit your previous Incident Report for Consumer (fr)
panelTitleHowToImport: Viewing or editing a previously saved Incident Report for Consumer(fr)
howToImportBullet1: From a blank form webpage (use F5/refresh to clear current form and refresh the page)(fr)
howToImportBullet2: Use 'Browse/Choose File' button on webpage to select previously saved .hcxs file.(fr)
howToImportBullet3: Directly below, click on the 'Upload Information' button.(fr)
howToImportBullet4: Previously saved information will be loaded into form.(fr)
howToImportBullet5: Edit, save and submit the information as desired.(fr)
